metadata.name: Cosmic Cleric of Circuits
metadata.description:
Cosmic Cleric of Circuits is representative of a new style I have been working on which is exemplified in my recent Ordinals collection Technophiles. Comprised of circuits and advanced technology, this piece explores that deep connection humans have formed with technology. 

This piece has been upscaled, yet you can stop by my Discord to obtain a 60-80MB version that has more detail. 

Website: https://gansy.art
Twitter: https:/twitter.com/thegansmachine
